<section class="py-20 px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-4xl dark:text-white">Product Management Is Complex. Sindre Makes It Manageable</h2>
    <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Juggling meetings, tasks, feedback, and strategy across multiple tools slows your team down. Misalignment, lost insights, and manual follow-ups drain your energy and delay impact.</p>
    <h3 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 md:text-3xl dark:text-white">Try it for yourself</h3>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="relative p-8 rounded-3xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50/80 to-gray-100/60 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white/20 to-transparent"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <textarea
              id="demo-textarea"
              class="w-full h-40 p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-white placeholder-gray-500 dark:placeholder-gray-400 resize-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-500 focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="Paste meeting notes, ideas, or tasks here...&#10;&#10;Example: 'We discussed the new user onboarding flow. Sarah mentioned users are confused about the account setup process. We need to simplify the form and add better guidance. Action item: Create wireframes for the new flow by Friday.'"
            ></textarea>

            <button id="analyze-btn" class="group inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-600 to-brand-400 max-w-xs mx-auto">
              Analyze with AI
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

